name: SnmpCollector
tagline: A full featured  Generic SNMP data collector with Web Administration Interface
body:
### Welcome to SnmpCollector

SnmpCollector is snmp data collector tool which sends data to an influxdb database. This tool is designed to be fast and easily configurable, thanks to its web User Interface.

### Authors and Contributors
 @toni-moreno and @sbengo

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with snmpcollector? Check out our [documentation](https://github.com/toni-moreno/snmpcollector/wiki)
